    <summary>Modern text editor with multi-format preview support</summary>
    <description>
Lala is a modern, lightweight text editor with both GUI and CLI interfaces built with Rust.

Features:
- File tree view with async loading
- Syntax highlighting for multiple programming languages
- Multi-format preview: Markdown, HTML, Mermaid diagrams, LaTeX documents
- Advanced search and replace with regex support
- Both CLI and GUI modes for flexible usage
- Pure Rust implementation with no WebView dependencies

The CLI mode allows you to preview Markdown, HTML, Mermaid, and LaTeX documents
directly in the terminal with beautiful formatting.
